data.description: Lovely, unique, and fun home! Extremely well taken care of, pride shows! Updated, 3 bed, bonus room, 2 bath home, on large corner lot, with newer roof. Entry into the home shows class w/ high ceilings, and a gorgeous custom framed fireplace facing living room, step upstairs to a large open concept kitchen, new LG appliances, reverse osmosis water system at kitchen sink/fridge, granite counters, cook in style at the center of your island/bar overlooking another statement piece is a fireplace to dine at, and doors leading to your back patio. Basement has primary bedroom w/ adjoining bath and french doors to your private patio, wired for hot tub. Decked out garage w/ mounted tv, and so much more.
